---
	import team_data from "../../data/soul-searcher-team.json";
	import Credits from "../../components/Credits.svelte";
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<title>Playmakers Dev Team</title>
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/style/global.css">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/style/games/soul-searcher.css">
</head>
<body>
	<main>
		<img id="banner" src="/assets/images/soul-searcher/banner.png" alt="Banner image of the soul searcher game">
		<div class="grid">
			<div class="text-container">
				<p><em>Soul Searcher</em> is a turn-based strategy game with procedurally generated dungeons where you have to delve through a dead man’s memories in order to find his soul. </p>
				<p>Create synergies between your team, become capable of overcoming increasingly difficult enemies, reap the rewards and perfect your dream-dwelling team.</p>
			</div>
			<a href="#">
				<button>Available on Itchi.io</button>
			</a>
			<img src="/assets/images/soul-searcher/spawn.gif" alt="">
		</div>
		
		<a href="#detail" class="fit">
			<img id="icon-point" src="/assets/icons/point.svg" alt="cursor">
		</a>
		
		<nav class>
			<a href="#socials">SOCIALS</a>
			<a href="#devlogs">DEVLOGS</a>
			<a href="#team">TEAM</a>
		</nav>
		
		<section id="detail" class="text-section">
			<h2>More</h2>
			<p>Venture solo into the depths of the human mind with characters themed around abstract human concepts such as ideologies, life values, and dream. You will get to explore fragments of a man's memories that have been twisted into hostile, surreal dungeons by an outside force.</p>
			<p>These adventures into the memory moiré entail:</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Levelling up and perk customization</li>
				<li>The wide array of characters and enemies</li>
				<li>Branching paths of mechanical and mental skills</li>
				<li>Bosses and relics to spice up the outcome and obstacles of your runs</li>
			</ul>
		</section>
		
		<section id="socials" class="text-section">
			<h2>Socials</h2>
			<div id="socials-container">
				<a href="https://discord.gg/CMD2YPG">
					<img src="/assets/icons/discord.svg" alt="Discord Logo">
				</a>
				<a href="https://www.facebook.com/Playmakers-Dev-Team-155950606557133">
					<img src="/assets/icons/facebook.svg" alt="Facebook Logo">
				</a>
				<a href="https://twitter.com/UTS_PDT">
					<img src="/assets/icons/twitter.svg" alt="Twitter Logo">
				</a>
				<a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@playmakersdevteam">
					<img src="/assets/icons/tiktok.svg" alt="TikTok Logo">
				</a>
				<a href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCLWR9n_BmFD0qNBgIoIyHog/featured">
					<img src="/assets/icons/youtube.svg" alt="YouTube Logo">
				</a>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section id="devlogs" class="text-section">
			<h2>Devlogs</h2>
			<p>More to come ;) ...</p>
		</section>
		

		<section id="team" class="text-section">
			<h2>Our Wonderful Team</h2>
			<Credits data={team_data} />
		</section>
		
	</main>
</body>
</html>
